snippet.title: WitchSpring3 30sec. for GooglePlay
snippet.description:
The story of a witch who is chased after by warriors. Eirudy, the Marionette Witch.
A story-based RPG with no additional in-app payments.

AppStore : https://itunes.apple.com/jp/app/%E9%AD%94%E5%A5%B3%E3%81%AE%E6%B3%893/id1298366657?mt=8

GooglePlay : https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.kiwiwalks.witchspring3
